{"id":126688,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：印度首都举行同性恋大游行/","date":"2010-11-28T22:32:26Z","modified":"2010-11-28T22:32:26Z","title":"简讯：印度首都举行同性恋大游行","content":"<div>\n<p>在印度首都德里，约两千人参加了同性恋大游行。</p>\n<p>这是自去年印度最高法院将同性恋合法化以来的首次游行。</p>\n<p>参加游行的活动人士和支持者有许多穿着色彩鲜艳的服装，挥舞彩虹旗和标语牌。</p>\n<p>一名组织者说，同性恋者希望显示他们也是社会中的一员，而大游行则是庆祝他们的与众不同。</p>\n<p>记者们说，同性恋在印度这样一个仍然非常保守的社会里还是会遭到蔑视的。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hCyVc__80vZM_Onruvsmvyhay9M/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hCyVc__80vZM_Onruvsmvyhay9M/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hCyVc__80vZM_Onruvsmvyhay9M/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/hCyVc__80vZM_Onruvsmvyhay9M/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=UjXt35CsSeo:mUVE6YUq58A:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/UjXt35CsSeo\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_bl